A trip can be constructed by choosing railings within a filtered selection, but how are we supposed to order these?
Routing algorithms usually involve providing a number of geographical points that you want to, in order, traverse.
The algorithm has to consider the direction of both the camera rig and the car.
List of railings within a geographical region, road no. & postal code? (E39, xxxx)
We need to seperate railings by direction and side, especially where the road has a middle railing.
